Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.44,0:00:05.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Fixed yesterday's 40 dollar bug with 3 lines of code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.83,0:00:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Then added a second witness that never sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.53,0:00:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}I can't code.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.90,0:00:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}9 years in crypto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.10,0:00:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}AI trades my thousand.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.33,0:00:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.69,0:00:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The fix was simple — replace my regular market sell with Coinbase's built-in close-position endpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.74,0:00:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It auto-detects direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.83,0:00:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Physically cannot leave a residual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Three lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}For me, three words.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.58,0:00:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}But the code fix alone wasn't the real answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.90,0:00:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}The reason yesterday's bug could hide for 5.5 hours — my monitoring system and the bot's brain were the same brain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.88,0:00:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}So I built one more thing — a reconciler that runs every 15 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.43,0:00:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It doesn't listen to what the bot says.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}It just compares two lists —
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}how many trades in the database?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}How many fills on Coinbase?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.69,0:01:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}If they don't match, it wakes me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.19,0:01:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Anything that matters — you need a second witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.62,0:01:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}One that doesn't share your assumptions.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Day 15 tomorrow — first clean profit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.06,0:01:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}Follow along.
